
Network monitoring and auto incident MONITORING tool
Network Monitoring  Automation Tool that Monitor Node’s IP and Generate Incident in with date time.
Network Monitoring Module check IP Address reachability
AND IF devices will Un-reachable application will generate
Auto-Incident in Application Page
Application will track Incident Information in this page and provide console to user to close the Incident Number after once Node IP Address Reachable.

Application Stop Close Process of unreachable devices.

IF 

Device Unreachable.

AND

Provide OUTPUT 

“DEVICE NOT REACHABLE”

Application Provide Console to Addition Node IP Address in Application with Device Criticality and Device Group.

AND Result Provide as CRITICALITY AND GROUPS.

